Subject: Implement the 'it sync' subcommand, to pull/push changes with an upstream repo
Issuer: Vincent Driessen <vincent@datafox.nl>
Date: 2009-05-20 06:59:08
Type: feature
Priority: 1
Weight: 6
Status: open
Assigned to: -

- SYNC_WITH = raw_input('Sync with who? ')
- git fetch $SYNC_WITH git-it
- CURR_BRANCH = ?
- git stash save --keep-index 'stashed temporarily by git-it to sync git-it branch'
- git co git-it
- git merge $SYNC_WITH/git-it
- git mergetool
- git push $SYNC_WITH git-it
- git co $CURR_BRANCH
- git stash pop
